core.​ XPS_typ_Enumeration

TypeDefinition

Authors

Crashdome

Description

Abstract Class. Helper that provides lookup and retrieval of global static enumerations.  Derived classes created with XPS_fnc_createEnumeration will store a type-safe set of enumeration references to global variables which are constants (compileFinal'd).

Parent

none

Implements

None

unscheduled
